stlib.operations.predicates.lifted

Class BaseAlgorithm

  • java.lang.Object
    • stlib.operations.predicates.lifted.BaseAlgorithm
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    InsidePointRegion

    public abstract class BaseAlgorithm
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract class that provides a basic algorithm using the template method pattern

    The algorithm runs through both passed 'MovingObject' and executes the specific operation on 'unit' level, where they overlap in their time period. The result is a 'MovingBool' object.

    getUnitResult - realizes the real operation on unit level, to implement by a subclass
    Author:
    Markus Fuessel
